welcomeSection.title: Welcome
welcomeSection.subtitle: Your Trusted Dentist in Fremont
welcomeSection.content: At Fremont Dental Smiles - Dr Jain we provide the services you and your loved ones need to enjoy a lifetime of healthy, beautiful smiles. Our friendly team understands each age brings its own set of dental issues so we welcome everyone from ages two and older to our office. We offer family dental appointments, allowing you to get your whole family in for their biannual exams at the same time.
welcomeSection.content2: Our dental practice is conveniently located on East Remington Drive and we proudly serve the residents of Sunnyvale and surrounding areas.
welcomeSection.content3: If you are looking for a dentist who can provide the array of treatments you need to safeguard your smile, then we are the place for you. Contact us today to shedule your appointment.

gentleDentistSection.title: Your Gentle Dentist in Fremont
gentleDentistSection.content: It should not be difficult to find a dentist who can provide the services you and your loved ones need. At Sunnyvale Family Smiles - Dr. Shazi, we combine modern techniques with a gentle chairside manner to give you the quality care you deserve. Wether your toddler needs their first visit, the senior in your family is interested in dentures, or you would like veneers to give you a stunning smile, we are here for you.
